After days of strike action, the National Association of Resident Doctors has called off the decision with effect from Monday, June 22, 2020. The announcement was made through a communique read to journalists by Dr Aliyu Sokomba, President of the group, on Sunday in Abuja after its National Executive Council meeting.Â 

